/**
 * @file IDM.rc
 * @brief Windows resource file for the IDM Clone application
 *
 * Contains: application icon, version information, dialog templates,
 * string tables, and manifest for visual styles.
 *
 * Note: In production, dialog templates would be designed in Visual Studio's
 * resource editor. Here we define minimal templates that are enhanced
 * programmatically in the dialog OnInitDialog() methods.
 */

